Discovered by: Aliaksandr Hartsuyeu (eVuln.com)

-----------------Description---------------
Cross-Site Scripting. 

Vulnerable Script: tag.php 

Parameter cjmsg is not properly sanitized. This can be used to post
arbitrary HTML or web script code. 



